reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Relieved to see so much quality in this bag
reviews.reviewText: I have sent two different bags with quality issues back to Amazon and am very pleased with this bag! The brown color is rich, the hardware, attractive and durable looking. I love that there are 3 generous, exterior zippered pockets for rushed moments for keys, phone, and my small wallet. The lining is good quality and the generous interior will hold notebooks, small umbrellas, my kindle and reports. I must have the cross shoulder strap for security and back comfort. The bag came well packed and padded. It is worth the wait (a bit over a week) and I expect this handsome bag to become my preferred bag. It is worth every penny.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful purse at a great price!!!
reviews.reviewText: This purse exceeded my expectations! Beautiful, spacious, well-made and NO funny smell. Very pleased with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love the size of the bag and length of the strap! The color is great as well! The only thing I don’t like is there is a distinct fishy smell on the inside. Hopefully this goes away after some time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love this bag!It has pockets everywhere and the sewing is wonderful (I quilt and sew a bit, and tend to look at seams) and the fabric is top notch. This feels like a high mid range bag and fits a lot of stuff - I am at that age where I carry my meds and my husband's meds everywhere, so I need space! This has it - and I am organized!The pictures don't do it justice, this is a prettier bag in person. I got the khaki, but it is a pretty beige. It did have a faint smell that dissipated after about a day (and I have a pretty keen sense of smell!) The lining feels thick - I love that quality fabric. The zippers are smooth. Even the vegan leather is nice.I would buy this again... and probably will in another color. Yup. Definitely a great bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This just might be "THE BAG" I've been looking for.
reviews.reviewText: Like many products created for women, we all have persnickety likes and dislikes, don't we? What I love about this bag, you may hate. I need a bag to hold "STUFF"! (That's said in a deep bass voice) You may prefer a hand clutch by Kate Spade. Personally, I don't see what the hoopla is about those. They hold nothing.See, we're all different.I am kinda picky about my purses that I spend actual money on. Recently, (like for the last 10 years) I been using a grocery tote. I just couldn't find style, color, or features for less than $100. I'm cheap. I don't want to cart around something that costs a bunch of money, I just want it to look like I am!I like everything about this purse with one exception. I like the faux leather. It is supple, soft and feels nice. It also looks nice. I like the BOHO style. I like the size of the bag. I mentioned my tote bags. I need space. I need pockets, I need zippers. I need my STUFF! This bag has a lot of stylish room. I like the heavy zippers. I don't think these zippers will give up due to hard use any time soon. I like the layout of the interior. THANK YOU FOR NOT MAKING THE INTEIOR BLACK. I have passed on many a purse because of black lining. I'd prefer a color other than gray, but it is such a huge step in the right direction that I'm not going to complain about that. I'm just so glad it isn't black. How do designers expect you to find anything in a cavernous bag with a black lining?? The interior has a middle zippered pouch and a zipper pocket on one side. It has two side zipper pouches that I didn't think I'd like, but I really, really do. it also has a back zipper pocket. I actually haven't found a use for that yet, since this purse is SO roomy. I like the handle that can be used as a hand hold or swung up onto the shoulder. I haven't used the longer one yet. I wanted this on my shoulder and tucked under my arm. It's perfect.My one complaint, and keep in mind this will not keep me from enjoying my new bag, is that it is a little heavy. All of that quality of materials costs in the weight of the bag. Then when I pack it with my STUFF, it gets heavier. I'm thinking I'll just build some "purse muscle" to deal with that little issue!Seriously, we all have our little picky things that keep us from liking one bag or another. This bag hits everything for me. I love the style, the quality, the roominess...I like it so much, I may buy another one and put it away for when this one finally gives up the ghost and becomes too ratty to use. It took me 30 years to find this bag. I imagine it would take me another 30 to replace it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Decent for the price
reviews.reviewText: Pros: stylish, roomy (yes you can carry your reading book with you), organization, seems durable, because its faux leather you don’t have to baby it or watch out for weatherCons: obviously its faux leather, lining is nylon, had a slight smell of pepper upon arrival that disappeared in about a week, purchased gold hardware and one of the zipper pulls was gun metal and didn’t match the rest, main zipper a little wonky in that you must hold it with one hand and unzip with other but it works.Let’s see how it holds up!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this purse!
reviews.reviewText: It’s so durable and a year later I am still using it almost everyday! It’s super roomy, easy to clean and has lots of inside pockets. I love that I can zip it closed. I can put a lot in it, Cary a large tablet in it and fly on a plane with a sweater in it too! The color is perfect and it’s so comfortable to wear. If I don’t fill it too much it’s not too heavy to carry.

reviews.reviewTitle: Lots of pockets, large and cute!
reviews.reviewText: Great bag! Perfect for carrying thing around hands free, and lots of room to add a few items for my kids while we’re out. The bag was slightly larger than I expected but, not enough I won’t use the bag. Originally bought this to use as a work bag, but it’s become my work bag and my everyday bag! There was no strong smell like others have mentioned. Lots of pockets to keep organized and the whole bag zips closed. The more I use this bag the more I love it!

reviews.reviewerName: No one else Like meNo one else Like me
reviews.reviewText: Die Handtasche ist wirklich schön und Dank Amazon auch super schnell gekommen. Ich habe sie in der Farbe Schwarz bestellt und bin von der Optik begeistert! Das Kunstleder fühlt sich gut an, ist weich und hat eine ganz leicht gerippte Optik, wodurch sie interessanter erscheint gegenüber einer Glattleder-Tasche. Sie hat von Anfang an, innen, genauso wie außen, neutral gerochen. Im Inneren der Tasche gibt es ein Mittelfach mit Reißverschluss, womit der Innenteil der Handtasche in 3 Teile geteilt wird, und womit man das mittlere Fach noch einmal extra für sich, schließen kann. Sie hat noch andere diverse kleine Fächer, damit alles schön geordnet ist und man wichtige Dinge, wie z.B. das Handy, oder andere Sachen, schnell findet. Die Verarbeitung ist perfekt, man sieht wirklich absolut keine Reste vom Kleber o.ä., außerdem gibt es auch keine Fäden die irgendwo raushängen, wirklich Nichts! Das Einzige, was man evtl. erwähnen kann ist folgendes, ein paar der goldenen Teile, also die Schieber des Reißverschlusses sind nicht aus Metall, sondern aus Kunststoff (meiner Meinung nach kein Mangel und mittlerweile wohl auch ganz normal bei der Produktion eines Reißverschlusses - wie man auf Wikipedia nachlesen kann, aber doch erwähnenswert).Mein Fazit: Ich liebe meine neue Handtasche und empfehle sie hiermit gerne an euch weiter.

Ho ricevuto la borsa che ho ordinato qualche giorno fa in tempo rapido e perfettamente confezionata.Aprendo la confezione ho piacevolmente costatato che il prodotto è veramente corrispondente a quanto descritto dal venditore. Non voglio soffermarmi sul modello di borsa da me ordinato, in quanto ritengo sia una valutazione molto soggettiva ma comunque molto bella ma voglio sottolineare la qualità della borsa che ritengo sia superiore alle mie aspettative.La pelle è molto morbida e piacevole al tatto, la lavorazione eseguita in maniera veramente perfetta, le cerniere oltre ad essere un tocco raffinato nell'insieme del design sono molto efficienti e scorrono benissimo. Aprendo l'interno è ampio e spazioso con alcuni spazi ricavati sulla parti interne che permettono di separare piccoli oggetti dagli altri per una facile gestione del contenuto il tutto foderato da una fodera lucida.Un ulteriore particolare oltre alle maniglie inserite nella borsa è la tracolla in aggiunta che è possibile applicare e togliere per poter eventualmente portare a tracolla.Prodotto ritenuto valido e consigliato.

L'intérieur contient plusieurs poches plaquées et une poche centrale qui permet de disposer de deux grands espaces de rangement bien distincts. De plus, il y a trois petites poches extérieures. Pour quelqu'un comme moi qui transporte toujours plein de choses différentes dans son sac à main, c'est idéal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on May 16, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: Vegan friendly! Comes with a cute surprise gift!
reviews.reviewText: I've been trying to find a casual slouchy handbag for ages and this one is perfect! Size is great, you can fit all your everyday essentials in - has three sections inside, with the middle one being a zipped pocket. Has two straps and the longer one is adjustable to preference which is fab.When I received the bag I looked through it to see what it was like and I came across a little handmade charm in the bottom of the bag which came with a card which stated that it was a handmade Chinese good luck/positivity charm which the seller/brand had included as an extra gift and that honestly made my day! Very sweet.I love the bag so much I've gone and ordered it again but in brown!! Definitely recommend!
